# Model routing (Cursor)

- **Default:** fast, execution-focused — small diffs, run tests, ship.
- **Go deep** when Ranne says "go deep", "think hard", "architecture", or "security review" — prefer stronger reasoning models for multi-file refactors and subtle bugs.
- **Do not** switch models for trivial one-line fixes.
- **Runtime Nami** (Telegram/Hermes) uses local Ollama on Mac — if the task needs full repo edits, say so and point Ranne to Cursor.

Config reference: `hermes-nami/model-routing.yaml`, skill `hermes-nami/skills/model-routing.md`.
